## Pricing Page Content (locked from research)

**3-Tier Table:**

| Tier | Name | Includes | Price (600 sq ft avg) | Per sq ft |
|------|------|----------|----------------------|-----------|
| 1 | Essential Restore | Power wash + 2-coat premium sealant | $299 | ~$0.45 |
| 2 | Premium Restore | Power wash + crack fill + edge sealing + 2-coat sealant | $499 | ~$0.75 |
| 3 | Complete Restore | Full assessment + Premium services + minor patching + UV topcoat + 3-year warranty | $849 | ~$1.10 |

**Add-ons:** Crack fill only $75-$150 / Oil stain treatment $50-$100 / Decorative edge banding $2.50/lin ft / Apron repair: quote required

**Key anchor copy:** "A new driveway costs $3,000-$8,000. Complete Restore: $849."

