## Scope Fence

**Build (demo-builder does this):**
- All 9 pages (8 + /free-estimate), mobile-first, sticky CTAs
- Working estimate form (Flask backend, real lead storage)
- Before/after drag slider (img-comparison-slider web component)
- Gallery with lightbox
- Service area map (Google Maps iframe)
- All JSON-LD schema (LocalBusiness, Service, FAQPage, AggregateRating, BreadcrumbList)
- GA4 event hooks (gtag snippets)
- sitemap.xml
- Unique title/meta/H1 per page, ALT text on all images
- Flask blueprint in mw-backend

**Describe in proposal only (not built in demo):**
- Actual WordPress + Bricks Builder deployment
- Rank Math, Fluent Forms, Wordfence, UpdraftPlus, ShortPixel, Site Kit (described as Phase 1 delivery tools)
- Google Business Profile optimization
- Actual Rocket.net hosting
- Phase 2 features

