## handoff
- produced: finalized 9-page plan (static demo + Flask backend), locked design system (charcoal #1A1D1A / forest-green #2F5D3A / off-white #F5F4F0, Playfair Display + Inter), feature map, traceability matrix, 3-tier pricing, competitor gap analysis, fortherecordmn.com proof framing, workSamples.js registry entry.
- decisions: static demo is primary build target (no WP Docker on critical path); Docker WP stretch is CEO-gated only; img-comparison-slider for before/after; CSS filter trick for before/after imagery; Flask blueprint for real lead capture; fortherecordmn.com proof cites deliverables not traffic numbers; Phase 1 price $1,100 fixed + Rocket 2 months.
- next needs: demo-builder to build all 9 pages (index.html + 8 inner) + sitemap.xml + Flask blueprint; proposal-writer to answer all 6 dev questions, use approved fortherecordmn.com framing, and set Phase 2 range at $3,500-$6,500.
- risks: img-comparison-slider CDN availability (fallback: vanilla JS drag implementation ~50 LOC); Docker WP on Surface unconfirmed (not critical path); before/after stock imagery may need CSS filter simulation (strategy locked above); client may ask for real WP login (proposal addresses this by describing the full WP delivery plan clearly).
